Package: uktax
Type: Package
Title: Functions for Calculating UK Tax and Benefits for Economic Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(c("Ian","K"), "Salter",  email = "ianksalter@gmail.com", 
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package creates classes for analysing the UK Tax
    and Benefit system from 2016. As of version 0.1.0 if focuses 
    soley on a single employed person as a simplification. The 
    package allows the easy calculation of taxation and benifit
    amounts based upon income.
